{
  "stem": "24242.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You think my brother, when he walks with an open machine gun, all he has to do is-- is-- is touch the trigger of the machine gun, and then people get killed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You think he had no fear?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, he had fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would assume I had fear, otherwise, why would I go and run away and hide myself when I saw they beat my father up?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I knew if he has a rifle, and he's there, I have to run the other way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I assume it's out of fear, is it not?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS] No.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In our area, when we came to-- to [NON-ENGLISH], that's where we heard about Polish partisans, but we really never came encounter with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only ones that were were the Russian partisans, and there was another Jewish small brigade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember in [NON-ENGLISH], he had about 150 people, women and children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a Jew that was born in Minsk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zorin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He is the only one that was in the-- there were little groups, like bandits.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were people like those that survived the war, like a group of 10, very few.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, they-- they were caught by the Russian partisans and brought to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the-- Yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At least.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were 4 or 500 young men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did everything later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lead together with the Russian partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- They would wait for a convoy with trucks, kill the Nazis as much as they could, and take their arms away and take whatever there was away from them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They burned bridges, they-- whatever they could, whatever they-- to hurt the Nazis, that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they were fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were orders from the higher ups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why it was divided.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
